---
title: Apricot-Glazed Chicken with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes and Carrots
description: Crispy-skinned chicken is delicious enough on its own, but we’re upping the ante even further with a sweet-and-spicy apricot glaze. A touch of sweet paprika gives this dish an unexpected smokiness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/apricot-glazed-chicken-88ec3238.jpg
